OL,7,FA firebrand orator and former
OL,8,FCelebrity Big Brother contestant, Mr
OL,9,FGalloway has enjoyed support from some
OL,10,Fleft-wing groups for his staunch
OL,11,Fsupport of Palestinian causes, but
OL,12,Fbeen accused of stoking division and
OL,13,Fusing sexist, homophobic and
OL,14,Fantisemitic language by his opponents.
