OL,3,CGeorge Galloway, a deeply divisive
OL,4,Cfigure in UK politics, returns to
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FIt was Palestine that formed the
OL,8,Fcornerstone of his campaign in
OL,9,FRochdale, where he became the
OL,10,Ffavourite after Labour withdrew
OL,11,Fsupport from its own candidate over
OL,12,Fremarks about the Israel-Hamas
OL,13,Fconflict.
OL,15,FAnd Palestine has been a major theme
OL,16,Fof Mr Galloway's political career, one
OL,17,Fmarked by ferocious opposition to
OL,18,FBritish and American foreign policies,
OL,19,Fboth in the Middle East and, more
OL,20,Frecently, in their support for Ukraine.
