OL,3,CGeorge Galloway, a deeply divisive
OL,4,Cfigure in UK politics, returns to
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FOne of his first political campaigns
OL,8,Fas a youthful Labour Party activist
OL,9,Fwas to press for his home town of
OL,10,FDundee to be twinned with Nablus on
OL,11,Fthe Palestinian West Bank.
OL,13,FHe first entered Parliament in 1987,
OL,14,Fwinning Glasgow Hillhead from former
OL,15,Fhome secretary and leading SDP figure
OL,16,FRoy Jenkins.
