OL,3,CGeorge Galloway, a deeply divisive
OL,4,Cfigure in UK politics, returns to
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FHis outspoken opposition to the 2003
OL,8,Finvasion of Iraq finally brought his
OL,9,Flong-running feud with the Labour
OL,10,Fhierarchy to a head.
OL,12,FHe was expelled from the party after
OL,13,Faccusing Tony Blair and George W Bush
OL,14,Fof acting "like wolves" and urging
OL,15,FBritish troops to disobey their
OL,16,F"illegal" orders.
