OL,3,CGeorge Galloway, a deeply divisive
OL,4,Cfigure in UK politics, returns to
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FHe went on to found the Respect party,
OL,8,Fdefeating Labour MP Oona King in
OL,9,FBethnal Green and Bow in 2005,
OL,10,Foverturning a 10,000 majority with a
OL,11,Fcampaign aimed at the East London
OL,12,Fconstituency's Bangladeshi community.
OL,14,FHe lost the seat in 2010, only to make
OL,15,Fan even more remarkable comeback two
OL,16,Fyears later taking Bradford West from
OL,17,FLabour in a by-election, after again
OL,18,Ftargeting the seat's largely Asian and
OL,19,FMuslim communities.
