OL,3,CGeorge Galloway, a deeply divisive
OL,4,Cfigure in UK politics, returns to
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FHe lost the seat again in 2015 after a
OL,8,Fcampaign that saw him accused of
OL,9,Fsexism against Labour's Naz Shah.
OL,11,FFurther bids for election came in the
OL,12,F2016 London mayoral contest, the 2017
OL,13,Fand 2019 general elections, and the
OL,14,F2021 Batley and Spen by-election, a
OL,15,Fcontest mired in claims of
OL,16,Fintimidation and homophobia.
