OL,3,CGeorge Galloway, a deeply divisive
OL,4,Cfigure in UK politics, returns to
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FAway from politics, he is perhaps best
OL,8,Fknown for his appearance on Celebrity
OL,9,FBig Brother in 2006, when he
OL,10,Fimpersonated a cat and pretended to
OL,11,Flick milk from the hands of another
OL,12,Fhousemate.
OL,14,FHe was also interrogated by a US
OL,15,FSenate committee in connection with
OL,16,Fclaims he had profited improperly from
OL,17,Ftrading in Iraqi oil, claims he denied
OL,18,Fin a fiery Senate hearing. He was
OL,19,Flater accused by the same committee of
OL,20,Flying under oath, which he again
OL,21,Fdenied.
